{"tid":1210884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐修例三毛威嚇中學校長","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:37:38.000Z","uid":52043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42cd128edca5814ab5c5c7bf5da797036b6458c4","tid":1210884,"uid":52043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:37:38.000Z","msg":"琴日間中學早會廣播容許學生罷課但前提係必須得到家長同意<br />\n0.3就打過去譴責校長並屈校長&rsquo;鼓吹&lsquo;學生罷課<br />\n之後係網上辱罵校長 教壞學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gd4tyMU_ugU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGd4tyMU_ugU&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=7f01bde9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gd4tyMU_ugU</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ze4Qzfn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZe4Qzfn.png&h=6baf94e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日朝早無線新聞訪問校長 <br />\n校長為了保護學生老師同學校聲譽<br />\n決定不容許罷課 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d005f18e60383310792ec81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d005f18e60383310792ec81&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=f196da50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d005f18e60383310792ec81</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfqwiG7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfqwiG7.png&h=7968313b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}